<h3>🚀 What You Can Do:</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>📝 Report Issues:</strong> Submit reports about problems in your community</li>
  <li><strong>📷 Add Photos:</strong> Upload photos to help describe the issue</li>
  <li><strong>📍 Pin Location:</strong> Use our map to pinpoint exact locations</li>
  <li><strong>💬 Add Comments:</strong> Communicate with barangay officials</li>
  <li><strong>📊 Track Progress:</strong> Monitor the status of your reports</li>
</ul>

<h3>📋 How to Report an Issue:</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Click "New Report"</strong> on the dashboard</li>
  <li><strong>Choose Category:</strong> Select the type of issue (flooding, road damage, etc.)</li>
  <li><strong>Select Barangay:</strong> Choose your barangay</li>
  <li><strong>Add Details:</strong> Describe the issue and upload photos</li>
  <li><strong>Pin Location:</strong> Use the map to show exact location</li>
  <li><strong>Submit:</strong> Your report will be sent to barangay officials</li>
</ol>

<%= link_to "Start Reporting Issues", root_url, class: "button" %>

